title: U.S. VP Harris says Russia must show it is serious about diplomacy - Reuters
content:

description: U.S. Vice President Kamala Harris met NATO Secretary General Jens Stoltenberg and leaders from three Baltic nations on Friday and said Russia must show it is open to diplomacy, while warning Moscow of severe consequences if it invades Ukraine.
